Collection of SMART COSMOS Objects context modeling artifacts.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IDevice
    Identifies a specific type of computation device and a means of uniquely identifying a specific device.
    IFile
    Represents any type of multimedia file that is explicitly associated with a single IReferentialObject.
    ILibraryElement
    Foundational artifact within the SMART COSMOS Objects platform used to represent nouns, e.g.
    IObject
    Foundational artifact within the SMART COSMOS Objects platform used to represent nouns, e.g.
    IObjectAddress
    Captures a political address for a specific IObject.
    IObjectInteraction
    Captures an explicit interaction between two existing IObject instances that already exist in the system.
    IObjectInteractionSession
    Simple construct used to establish a logical albeit arbitrarily defined peer relationship between a collection of IObjectInteraction instances.
    IRelationship
    Captures binary or true-false conditions between objects.
    ITag
    Defines a word or phrase useful for searching across related objects.
    ITagAssignment
    Captures a ITag assignment with a specific IReferentialObject within a specific account context.
    ITimelineEntry
    Defines a historically significant event identified by name and a specific timestamp, optionally clarified by an optional description.

Package net.smartcosmos.objects.model.context Description

Collection of SMART COSMOS Objects context modeling artifacts. The interfaces and enumerations within this package form the foundation for the major contextual object model components.
